headline: Looking At The UDR Narrative As Analyst Views And Fair Value Gradually Shift
summary: The latest update to the UDR narrative reflects only a very small change in the modeled fair value, with the estimate moving from about US$40.36 to about US$40.38 per share as analysts fine tune their assumptions. That slight adjustment is tied to research suggesting a more constructive tone around Coastal Apartment REITs in the period leading up to 2026, where some firms are revisiting targets in light of evolving views on sector conditions and potential total return ranges. headline: Do Wall Street Analysts Like UDR Stock?
summary: UDR has significantly lagged the broader market over the past year, yet analysts remain cautiously optimistic about its future prospects.
